{"tid":979931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲長髮女郎搭巴士瞓覺 慘遭後排老翁剪頭髮","createTime":"2019-01-13T06:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T06:23:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1444e1636e8832eac18931a51537a55278e612","tid":979931,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190113/_2019011314063739285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190113%2F_2019011314063739285.jpg&h=28568679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣發生巴士女乘客被男乘客無故剪頭髮案件。<br />\n<br />\n早上9時，一輛107號線城巴由九龍灣開往香港仔期間，上層一名束長髮的25歲女乘客在座位打瞌睡，頭髮懷疑接觸到後面一名男乘客，對方心有不滿，未有作出投訴就取出剪刀剪斷女乘客十多厘米長髮。其他乘客見狀慌忙通知女事主，並制止男乘客，並報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方早上9時接報，指25歲姓丁女乘客，在景隆街及告士打道交界對開一輛巴士上懷疑被65歲姓余男乘客襲擊。警員接報到場，經初步調查，男子涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害被捕，案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n城巴方面指，城巴駛出紅隧往銅鑼灣時，有乘客通知車長，上層一名乘客被另一名乘客用剪刀剪去頭髮，上層乘客合力制服乘客及報警。車長將巴士駛往景隆街巴士站停下了解及通知公司，警方到場處理。車上約有100人，乘客被安排轉乘其他車輛繼續行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1409316/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1409316%2F&d=cNQCUWuAuUgGHXOevH1H0C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e838535f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1409316%2F&h=57972023\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1409316/</a>"},{"pid":"dbc904c1a27b3ed4a973f3ea8f00802c723460ac","tid":979931,"uid":172950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:18:12.000Z","msg":"廢老......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7053598b194bf0b6f754ab99aa1f85996ad6846","tid":979931,"uid":27870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad893e377c304a87bc83046512e1c3691997528e","tid":979931,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"廢中"}]}